<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Slideshow Example</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    /* Navbar Styling */
    .navbar {
      position: absolute; /* Ensure the navbar is always on top */
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between; /* Push content to edges */
      align-items: center; /* Vertically center items */
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      padding: 10px;
      z-index: 10; /* Ensure navbar is above the banner */
    }

    /* Styling for the logo on the left */
    .navbar .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .navbar .logo img {
      height: 40px; /* Adjust the height of the logo */
      width: auto; /* Ensure the aspect ratio is maintained */
    }

    .navbar .logo span {
      font-size: 1.5em;
      color: white;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-left: 10px;
    }

    /* Navbar button form styling */
    .navbar form {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-right: 15px;
    }

    /* Button styling */
    .navbar button {
      color: white;
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      border: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    /* Hover effect for buttons */
    .navbar button:hover {
      background-color: #45a049;
    }

    /* Banner Styling */
    .banner {
      position: relative; /* Position elements inside the banner */
      width: 100%;
      height: 400px; /* Height of the banner */
      background: url('your-banner-image.jpg') no-repeat center center;
      background-size: cover;
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      flex-direction: column; /* Arrange items in a vertical column */
    }

    .banner .banner-content {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .banner h1 {
      font-size: 36px; /* Adjust font size for the title */
      margin: 0 0 20px; /* Add margin below the title */
    }

    .banner p {
      font-size: 18px; /* Adjust font size for the description */
      margin: 0 0 20px; /* Add margin below the paragraph */
    }

    .banner .button-container {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 20px;
      right: 20px;
    }

    .banner button {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      color: #4CAF50;
      border: none;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      font-size: 16px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .banner button:hover {
      background-color: #45a049;
      color: white;
    }

    .container {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    /* Container for the slideshow */
    .slideshow-container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 800px; /* Adjust the max width as needed */
      margin: auto;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* Hide the images initially */
    .slides {
      display: flex;
      transition: transform 1s ease-in-out;
    }

    /* Style for each individual image */
    .slide {
      min-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
    }

    /* Style for the navigation buttons */
    .prev, .next {
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      width: auto;
      padding: 16px;
      margin-top: -22px;
      color: white;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 18px;
      transition: 0.3s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      border: none;
      border-radius: 50%;
      z-index: 100;
    }

    .prev {
      left: 0;
    }

    .next {
      right: 0;
    }

    .prev:hover, .next:hover {
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
    }

    /* Optional: Add dots for navigation (indicators) */
    .dot-container {
      text-align: center;
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 10px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
    }

    .dot {
      height: 15px;
      width: 15px;
      margin: 0 4px;
      background-color: #bbb;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: inline-block;
      transition: background-color 0.6s ease;
    }

    .active {
      background-color: #717171;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Navigation Bar -->
    <div class="navbar">
      <!-- Logo on the left side -->
      <div class="logo">
        <img src="logo.png" alt="Turtle Shelter Logo">
        <span>Turtle Shelter</span>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Navbar Buttons (aligned to the right) -->
      <div class="nav-buttons">
        <form action="/" method="GET">
          <button type="submit">Home</button>
        </form>
        <form action="/eventManagement" method="GET">
          <button type="submit">Event Management</button>
        </form>
        <form action="/volunteerForm" method="GET">
          <button type="submit">Volunteer Form</button>
        </form>
        <form action="/EventRequestForm" method="GET">
          <button type="submit">Event Request</button>
        </form>
        <form action="/volunteerManagement" method="GET">
          <button type="submit">Volunteer Management</button>
        </form>
        <form action="/adminLogin" method="GET">
          <button type="submit">Admin Login</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <!-- Banner Section -->
    <div class="banner">
      <div class="banner-content">
        <h1>Welcome to Turtle Shelter</h1>
        <p>Helping the homeless survive harsh winters with innovative technology.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="button-container">
        <button>Learn More</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Welcome to the Turtle Shelter Project</h1>
      <h1>Who we are</h1>
      <p>TSP is your organization dedicated to bringing homeless people the protection they need through high-tech winter vests.</p>
      <p>One winter when Jen was homeless, 7 of her friends froze to death. After surmounting her own journey from the frigid cold, she was determined to figure out a solution to help others with this burden. She created an inexpensive high-tech solution with the help of a survival expert that helps SAVE lives and more importantly alleviate suffering.</p>
      <p>There is no need for those in a state of emergency to have to pay so much on top of the burden of recovering.</p>
      <br>
      <h1>What we do</h1>
      <p>We answer the call to spread warmth in the lives of the homeless who are vulnerable to harsh winters by creating portable "shelters" that they can carry with them, just like a turtle.</p>
      <p>Although increased homeless services, especially additional shelter availability, are necessary to accommodate the amplified need in the winter, life-threatening hypothermia can set in between 32-50 degrees, which is not cold enough for many winter shelters to open.</p>
      <p>Our technology is about more than just making sure that the wearer maintains heat from their core. The warmth that our vests provide restores confidence, energy, and hope.</p>
      <h1>How you can help</h1>
      <b><p>"Every life has value, every person can serve", and you can take the next step to donate, make vests, and organize an event too!</p></b>
      <P>Be a part of a powerful campaign that changes lives of those in need.</P>
    </div>
  
</body>
</html>
